---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.jsx';
import Divider from '../components/Divider.jsx';

import '../styles/init.css';
---

<Layout title='Tiny Visions - Readings'>
  <main class='bg-palette-c-dark text-palette-c-light'>
    <Navbar client:load />
    <Divider />
    <header class='text-center mx-8 md:w-1/2 md:m-auto'>
      <h2 class='text-2xl my-6 font-bold text-palette-c-accent'>Readings</h2>
      <p class='text-left'>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Consectetur libero id faucibus nisl tincidunt eget nullam non. Blandit aliquam etiam erat velit scelerisque in dictum. At urna condimentum mattis pellentesque id. Dui accumsan sit amet nulla facilisi morbi tempus iaculis.
      </p>
    </header>
    <section class='mt-6 text-center md:w-1/2 md:mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-1 items-center justify-center'>
      <button class='rounded-sm w-1/2 py-2 px-4 md:mx-2 bg-palette-c-accent text-palette-c-light'>
        one card reading
      </button>
      <button class='rounded-sm w-1/2 py-2 px-4 md:mx-2 bg-palette-c-accent text-palette-c-light'>
        three card reading
      </button>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>